       The defocused helio particles beam can be safely entered by humans.

       Humans in a  defocused  beam,  take  on a very high concentration of
       soft particle electrons;  a high  negative  or  antigravity  charge.
       Thus, one may  now perform levitation, "water walking"  or  "flying"
       feats to amaze the uninitiated.

       The above technological  feats are independent of religious or moral
       systems.  High technology  is  neither   good   or  bad.   Only  the
       utilization of such technology determines those qualities.

